                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-260-victim1451 t18280911-260-viclabel1335"></join>. On the 17th of July, at nine o'clock at night, I lost a pair of trousers, which I had seen about half an hour before.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280911-260-person1452">
                  JAMES 
                  NOBLE
               <interp inst="t18280911-260-person1452" type="surname" value="NOBLE"></interp>
